The work of the organizer has brought the concept of using auspicious beliefs.

00:00:22.250 --> 00:00:25.250
of Thai people of Chinese descent to participate in the design

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:28.250
In terms of the sculpture's shape, it imitates

00:00:28.250 --> 00:00:31.250
the octagonal lantern made of paper.

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:37.250
Which he will be used to decorate the house to invoke auspiciousness into the house.

00:00:37.250 --> 00:00:41.250
or decorated along a long trade area to create an atmosphere that attracts customers to enter the store

00:00:41.250 --> 00:00:47.250
Lanterns often have decorations that convey auspicious things,

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:52.250
such as Chinese characters with good meanings. various auspicious animals on paper

00:00:52.459 --> 00:00:55.250
whether it's printing, drawing or stenciling.

00:00:55.250 --> 00:00:59.250
The organizer has brought to imitate the octagonal lamp

00:00:59.250 --> 00:01:05.250
to be larger. As a door arch used to decorate by stenciling

00:01:05.250 --> 00:01:12.250
by a metal stencil Using Chinese paper-cutting techniques

00:01:12.250 --> 00:01:18.250
which is unique, openwork pattern, 4 directions, leading to ancient astronomy of China

00:01:18.250 --> 00:01:20.250
in dividing the sky into 4 parts,

00:01:20.250 --> 00:01:23.750
namely North, South, East and West

00:01:23.750 --> 00:01:30.750
, with the animals of the direction representing auspicious meaning on the wall

00:01:30.750 --> 00:01:35.750
by this wall There are decorations as follows.

00:01:35.750 --> 00:01:38.750
There is a "black turtle" as the animal of the north. Representing the element of water

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:45.750
and winter, decorated with water waves and flowers, regular lotuses,

00:01:45.750 --> 00:01:49.750
representing stability, longevity, happiness

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:55.750
"Red Swan" is the animal of the south. Representative of the element of fire and summer

00:01:55.750 --> 00:01:57.750
The pattern is similar to the sun.

00:01:57.750 --> 00:02:03.750
the nature of the swan where there will be a flame Which represents rebirth, a

00:02:03.750 --> 00:02:07.750
symbol of good fortune, wealth, decorated with plum blossoms,

00:02:11.750 --> 00:02:16.750
"Green Dragon", the animal of the East. Representative of the wood and spring elements

00:02:16.750 --> 00:02:21.750
decorated with patterns cut peonies and lace

00:02:21.750 --> 00:02:28.750
chinese green dragon The head is a kirin, the body is a snake, and the tail is a fish,

00:02:28.750 --> 00:02:31.750
symbolizing prestige, honor and prosperity.

00:02:31.750 --> 00:02:36.750
The white tiger is the animal of the west. Representing the golden element,

00:02:36.750 --> 00:02:40.750
autumn, the pattern is a gold coin. and chrysanthemums

00:02:40.750 --> 00:02:46.750
The white tiger represents the protector and power. protection reverence

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:51.750
The gable of the sculpture arch brings the character of a Chinese shrine.

00:02:51.750 --> 00:02:56.750
which takes into account the matter of direction and elements in the design as well

00:02:58.750 --> 00:03:01.750
The meeting of auspicious animals from these four directions is

00:03:01.750 --> 00:03:03.750
like a combination of happiness.

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:09.250
Prosperity, longevity, fortune, wealth, prestige and power

00:03:09.250 --> 00:03:16.250
In addition, Chinese characters used to decorate the four directions will have a good meaning.

00:03:16.250 --> 00:03:19.250
which will create a good meaning for those who visit as well

00:03:19.250 --> 00:03:25.250
Lighting design, the designer has used the concept of lighting.

00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:30.250
that uses light to help both during the day and at night

00:03:30.250 --> 00:03:33.250
During the day, use direct natural light.

00:03:33.250 --> 00:03:38.250
sunlight shining through the sculpture This will cause the surrounding area to shadow,

00:03:38.250 --> 00:03:42.250
follow the stencil, and change at different times.

00:03:42.250 --> 00:03:47.250
During the night, it uses RGB lamps

00:03:47.250 --> 00:03:50.250
which are installed in the center of the pillars,

00:03:50.250 --> 00:03:53.250
like yellow dragon pillars, golden dragon pillars,

00:03:53.250 --> 00:03:56.250
and the patterns of movement colors,

00:03:56.250 --> 00:04:01.250
brightness can be changed according to the installed program.

